posts.name: Nick Foote
posts.cooked:
Yes they are! They look like they came out of the Lego factory, I love them. New foam rules mean we can use better materials.

IMG20250205160759 1920Ã—1440 280 KB

IMG20250205160759 1920Ã—1440 280 KB

IMG20250205160759 1920Ã—1440 280 KB

Harder foam on the outside, softer foam on the inside. When the outer foam gets hit, it spread the impact out over the softer foam and absorbs the hit better.
